Overview
===========================

The dns service listen for start/terminate instances and update dns 
server accordingly.


Configuration
===========================

Check config.html for details 

RPM Building
===========================

Clone nova-dns git repository, rename the top dir to nova-dns-VERSION,
and tar it to nova-dns-VERSION.tar.gz. Place it to rpmbuild/SOURCES
directory and run::

    $ rpmbuild -ba nova-dns.spec


Quickstart
===========================

Check quickstart.html for details

